      "id": "PopularPost35198",
      "post_content": "4 CC is great for this very versitile card. I love having this card in a discard deck. Instant [Hymn to Tourach](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Hymn to Tourach) and [Mind Twist](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mind Twist) is incredibly evil! You can even get a first turn Vedalkin Orrery if you have a draw with an Orrery, a Swamp, a [Dark Ritual](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Dark Ritual) and a [Sol Ring](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Sol Ring). ",
      "posted_by": "Pantheon",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost35198\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_post\">4 CC is great for this very versitile card.   I love having this card in a discard deck.  Instant <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Hymn to Tourach\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Hymn to Tourach\">Hymn to Tourach</a> and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Mind Twist\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mind Twist\">Mind Twist</a> is incredibly evil! You can even get a first turn Vedalkin Orrery if you have a draw with an Orrery, a Swamp, a <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Dark Ritual\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Dark Ritual\">Dark Ritual</a> and a <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Sol Ring\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Sol Ring\">Sol Ring</a>. </span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '35198'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy2775\">Pantheon</span>\r\n                                (11/13/2009 12:14:15 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent