    {
      "id": "PopularPost70918",
      "post_content": "@originalcardtext: [Hymn to Tourach](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Hymn to Tourach) won't work with [isochron scepter](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=isochron scepter) since it says it needs an instant card to be imprinted, also to be specific cycling is an activated ability  \n  \nThe only thing I can see how this is useful is instant speed discard and your sorcery removals to be used as spot removals ie. [Flame Slash](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Flame Slash). Other than that [Teferi, Mage of Zhalfir](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Teferi, Mage of Zhalfir) is better (although he's blue and the orrery is an artifact, makes his use a little bitmore limited).",
      "posted_by": "klauth",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost70918\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_post\">@originalcardtext: <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Hymn to Tourach\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Hymn to Tourach\">Hymn to Tourach</a> won't work with <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"isochron scepter\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=isochron scepter\">isochron scepter</a> since it says it needs an instant card to be imprinted, also to be specific cycling is an activated ability<br/><br/>The only thing I can see how this is useful is instant speed discard and your sorcery removals to be used as spot removals ie. <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Flame Slash\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Flame Slash\">Flame Slash</a>. Other than that <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Teferi, Mage of Zhalfir\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Teferi, Mage of Zhalfir\">Teferi, Mage of Zhalfir</a> is better (although he's blue and the orrery is an artifact, makes his use a little bitmore limited).</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '70918'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy17504\">klauth</span>\r\n                                (5/4/2010 8:07:36 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div