    {
      "id": "PopularPost182995",
      "post_content": "I was never a fan of [Leyline of Anticipation](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Leyline of Anticipation), and this card doesn't seem any better. I guess this is colorless, but you always have to pay 4 mana for it, so it doesn't seem very useful.  \n  \nTo all those people out there talking about instant speed hymns and mind twists, that seems quite unnecessary. Hymn and Mind twist are already backbreaking to begin with, (Mind twist is even banned in every competitive format other then vintage, which has far more broken things going on) so the idea of making it instant speed seems redundant, especially since you should have cast them before you reached the 4 mana needed to cast this. By turn 5, your opponent will have already hit most of their land drops and you don't have as high of a chance of screwing them over with the random discard. [Hymn to Toarch](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Hymn to Toarch) is just a 1 mana less [Mind Rot](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mind Rot) when they have 2 cards in hand. You want to cast Hymn as soon as possible so you have a chance of land scr... [(see all)](javascript:void(0);)",
      "posted_by": "Shiny_Espeon",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost182995\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_post\">I was never a fan of <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Leyline of Anticipation\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Leyline of Anticipation\">Leyline of Anticipation</a>, and this card doesn't seem any better. I guess this is colorless, but you always have to pay 4 mana for it, so it doesn't seem very useful.<br/><br/>To all those people out there talking about instant speed hymns and mind twists, that seems quite unnecessary.  Hymn and Mind twist are already backbreaking to begin with, (Mind twist is even banned in every competitive format other then vintage, which has far more broken things going on) so the idea of making it instant speed seems redundant, especially since you should have cast them before you reached the 4 mana needed to cast this. By turn 5, your opponent will have already hit most of their land drops and you don't have as high of a chance of screwing them over with the random discard. <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Hymn to Toarch\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Hymn to Toarch\">Hymn to Toarch</a> is just a 1 mana less <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Mind Rot\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mind Rot\">Mind Rot</a> when they have 2 cards in hand. You want to cast Hymn as soon as possible so you have a chance of land scr... <a href=\"javascript:void(0);\" onclick=\"ExpandPost(event, this, 182995)\">(see all)</a></span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '182995'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy46104\">Shiny_Espeon</span>\r\n                                (7/28/2011 1:09:30 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"5.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/>\n<br/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    \u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>"
    },
